{"tid":2096740,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"MNET仆街死","createTime":"2020-07-06T10:15:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T11:09:20.000Z","uid":143093,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9eb24ef40f737ed7d4a32389f076246c320be018","tid":2096740,"uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T10:15:00.000Z","msg":"【StarNews獨家】Red Velvet-IRENE&amp;SEULGI新曲MV被判定為十九禁，因具有煽情性<br />\n<br />\n6日，據starnews獨家報導，Red Velvet小分隊IRENE&amp;SEULGI首張迷你專輯《Monster》主打曲《Monster》MV被Mnet判定為十九禁。被判定十九禁的理由是具有煽情性。此前通過《Monster》MV預告視頻展現了強烈的表演與華麗的造型。因認為部分的場面過於露骨，所以做出了這樣的決定。<br />\n所屬公司SMTOWN娛樂公司表示:&ldquo;目前正在對相關部分進行修改並重新進行審議。<br />\n<br />\n又逼害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d22a58ef8cdb94986ad823a595c19c90d59883b7","tid":2096740,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T10:18:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8487866c221329ec4ac026acd9e68a0bfb3e3cc4","tid":2096740,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T10:19:22.000Z","msg":"具有煽情性？？？？？？"},{"pid":"36a0f8e3fbf2e8fd593fe729b967b28f94d94c3d","tid":2096740,"uid":68926,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T10:19:31.000Z","msg":"班大陸仔作出黎<br />\nstarnews冇出過依篇文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5432dd5e7a71f44e7844bc7d4b69141ab1f4be51","tid":2096740,"uid":152432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T10:19:45.000Z","msg":"OnL9???"},{"pid":"1b980685b51369b51313978981451216a7d0b16f","tid":2096740,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T10:19:53.000Z","msg":"要屌都屌SM啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83dc3d559a346853ad3ac006e18f4d3712e91ad0","tid":2096740,"uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"36a0f8e3fbf2e8fd593fe729b967b28f94d94c3d","tid":2096740,"u